Title: Relates to the dispensing of contraceptive drugs and devices that are self-administered
Summary: Relates to the dispensing of contraceptive drugs and devices that are self-administered; authorizes a licensed physician, certified nurse practitioner, and a licensed midwife to prescribe and order a non-patient specific regimen to a professional nurse and a licensed pharmacist for the dispensing of contraceptive drugs and devices that are self-administered.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the dispensing of contraceptive drugs and devices that are self-administered
